QuestData.Title: Send the Fleet
QuestData.Description:
This war has cost us dearly, but victory will soon be in our grasp.
What remains of the Horde fleet has departed Zuldazar and our spies say that the Banshee Queen's hand sails at their helm.
This is our chance, $n! With one strike we can eliminate what remains of their fleet and rid Azeroth of Blightcaller's filth once and for all!
The fleet is preparing to depart, report to the Harbormaster when you are ready to set sail.
QuestData.LogDescription: Speak to Harbormaster Cyrus Crestfall to set sail.

Objectives.Objective: Speak to Harbormaster Cyrus Crestfall to set sail
